<article class="row hentry post-260293 to4_article_post type-to4_article_post status-publish has-post-thumbnail category-op-ed tag-corporate-taxes tag-estate-tax tag-progressive-taxation tag-redistribution-of-wealth tag-taxes tag-universal-basic-income tag-wealth-inequality tag-wealth-tax section-economy-and-labor primary_topic-economy" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/ReportageNewsArticle">
<div class="small-12 medium-4 columns">
<a class="archive-image" href="https://truthout.org/articles/some-states-are-expanding-taxes-on-the-wealthy/" title="Some States Are Expanding Taxes on the Wealthy">
<img width="400" height="300" src="https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/2019_0711-taxes-400x300.jpg" class="attachment-sd_medium size-sd_medium" alt="States are responding to wealth concentration by closing loopholes and ending special tax benefits." loading="lazy" srcset="https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/2019_0711-taxes-400x300.jpg 400w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/2019_0711-taxes-200x150.jpg 200w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/2019_0711-taxes-800x600.jpg 800w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/2019_0711-taxes-1200x900.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px" />
</a>
</div>
<div class="small-12 medium-8 columns archive-text">
<div class="before-headline">
<div class='categories'>
<a href='https://truthout.org/category/news/' rel='category' class='news'>News</a>
</div>
<div class='sections'>
<a href='https://truthout.org/section/economy-and-labor/' rel='section' class='economy-and-labor' style='color: #2c5b53;'>Economy &amp; Labor</a>
</div>
</div>
<div class="">
<h2 class="entry-title" itemprop="headline">
<a href="https://truthout.org/articles/some-states-are-expanding-taxes-on-the-wealthy/">Some States Are Expanding Taxes on the Wealthy</a>
</h2>
</div>
<div class="entry-summary" itemprop="description">
<div>
<div class="entry-summary">States are responding to wealth concentration by closing loopholes and ending special tax benefits.</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="entry-meta">
<dl class="article__authors byline">
<dt class="meta-label">by </dt>
<dd class="author vcard" itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"><span itemprop="name"><a class="url fn" href="https://truthout.org/authors/elizabeth-mcnichol/" itemprop="url" rel="author">Elizabeth McNichol</a></span>, </dd>
<dd class="source org" itemprop="sourceOrganization" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Organization"><span itemprop="name"><a href='https://www.cbpp.org/blog/states-expanding-opportunity-through-wealth-taxes' itemprop='url'>Center on Budget and Policy Priorities</a></span></dd>
</dl>
<time class="published updated meta-data" datetime="2019-07-11T14:36:10+00:00" itemprop="datePublished dateCreated" content="2019-07-11T14:36:10+00:00">July 11, 2019</time>
<div class="hide" itemprop="publisher" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Organization">
<a href="https://truthout.org" itemprop="url">
<span itemprop="name">
Truthout
</span>
</a>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</article>
<article class="row hentry post-260293 to4_article_post type-to4_article_post status-publish has-post-thumbnail category-op-ed tag-corporate-taxes tag-estate-tax tag-progressive-taxation tag-redistribution-of-wealth tag-taxes tag-universal-basic-income tag-wealth-inequality tag-wealth-tax section-economy-and-labor primary_topic-economy" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/OpinionNewsArticle">
<div class="small-12 medium-4 columns">
<a class="archive-image" href="https://truthout.org/articles/progressive-taxes-only-go-so-far-pre-tax-income-is-the-problem/" title="Progressive Taxes Only Go So Far. Pre-Tax Income Is the Problem.">
<img width="400" height="300" src="https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/GettyImages-1032942004-400x300.jpg" class="attachment-sd_medium size-sd_medium" alt="Jeff Bezos, founder and CEO of Amazon, speaks to members of the Economic Club during their Milestone Celebration Event in Washington, DC, on September 13, 2018." loading="lazy" srcset="https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/GettyImages-1032942004-400x300.jpg 400w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/GettyImages-1032942004-200x150.jpg 200w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/GettyImages-1032942004-800x600.jpg 800w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/GettyImages-1032942004-1200x900.jpg 1200w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/GettyImages-1032942004-2400x1800.jpg 2400w" sizes="(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px" />
</a>
</div>
<div class="small-12 medium-8 columns archive-text">
<div class="before-headline">
<div class='categories'>
<a href='https://truthout.org/category/op-ed/' rel='category' class='op-ed'>Op-Ed</a>
</div>
<div class='sections'>
<a href='https://truthout.org/section/economy-and-labor/' rel='section' class='economy-and-labor' style='color: #2c5b53;'>Economy &amp; Labor</a>
</div>
</div>
<div class="">
<h2 class="entry-title" itemprop="headline">
<a href="https://truthout.org/articles/progressive-taxes-only-go-so-far-pre-tax-income-is-the-problem/">Progressive Taxes Only Go So Far. Pre-Tax Income Is the Problem.</a>
</h2>
</div>
<div class="entry-summary" itemprop="description">
<div>
<div class="entry-summary">We must restructure the market factors that have led to income inequality in the first place.</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="entry-meta">
<dl class="article__authors byline">
<dt class="meta-label">by </dt>
<dd class="author vcard" itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"><span itemprop="name"><a class="url fn" href="https://truthout.org/authors/dean-baker/" itemprop="url" rel="author">Dean Baker</a></span>, </dd>
<dd class="source org" itemprop="sourceOrganization" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Organization"><span itemprop="name"><a href='https://truthout.org' itemprop='url'>Truthout</a></span></dd>
</dl>
<time class="published updated meta-data" datetime="2019-02-04T15:48:03+00:00" itemprop="datePublished dateCreated" content="2019-02-04T15:48:03+00:00">February 4, 2019</time>
<div class="hide" itemprop="publisher" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Organization">
<a href="https://truthout.org" itemprop="url">
<span itemprop="name">
Truthout
</span>
</a>
